{"data":[{"date":"17:24 19/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua \u201cPogba Serbia\u201d?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/9/day-doi-bong-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-pogba-serbia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. T\u1edd Tuttosport tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU t\u1eeb b\u1ecf vi\u1ec7c theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Milinkovic-Savic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Milinkovic-Savic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Lazio. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n, anh ph\u00e2n ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n d\u00e0i c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/9/Hernan-Crespo-phat-bieu-ve-Sergej-Milinkovic-Savic-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU t\u1eeb b\u1ecf theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Milinkovic-Savic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua anh t\u1ea1o ra r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0 c\u0169ng ghi t\u1edbi 14 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 Europa League.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn. MU l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1t khao ng\u00f4i sao 23 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t, Mourinho nh\u1eafm Savic nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Carrick.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-nang-gia-hoi-mua-milinkovicsavic-len-100-trieu-bang-172-186876.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU h\u1ecfi mua Milinkovic-Savic</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 80 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Lazio li\u00ean t\u1ee5c t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Man \u0111\u1ecf ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 b\u1ecf cu\u1ed9c. Mirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 23 tu\u1ed5i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Milinkovic-Savic?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Juventus mua Milinkovic-Savic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u0111ang l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. T\u1edd Tuttosport tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Lazio v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" title=\"Sergej Milinkovic-Savic\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/16/Igli-Tare-phat-bieu-ve-Milinkovic-Savic-va-su-that-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Milinkovic-Savic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, BL\u0110 Juventus \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec3 HLV Massimiliano Allegri mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u01b0u ti\u00ean n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Milinkovic-Savic c\u1ee7a Lazio.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJuventus \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Lazio, sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Lazio nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Serbia. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 khi Milinkovic-Savic tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Juventus. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Serie A, anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3711","checkdouble":"188943"},{"date":"15:05 19/06","title":"M\u1edbi t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 v\u00ec ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/tang-tien-bi-phat-nang-vi-tiep-tuc-choi-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh vi th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi t\u00e1i xu\u1ea5t sau \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 nh\u01b0ng ngay \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha \u0111\u1ea1p th\u1eb3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0ng Ewonde (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng). C\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Ewonde n\u1eb1m s\u00e2n nh\u01b0ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u1ec9 r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u1eb7ng v\u00ec ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/tang-tien-bi-phat-nang-vi-tiep-tuc-choi-tho-bao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u0103ng do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ea5u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i cho h\u00e0nh vi c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a HAGL s\u1ebd b\u1ecb c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u hai tr\u1eadn ti\u1ebfp theo \"do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ewonde Epassi Louis Christian\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HAGL g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng HAGL, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/hlv-minh-phuong-that-vong-vi-hagl-bat-dau-da-tieu-xao-291-188742.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng) c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</span></span> khi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HAGL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u h\u1ecdc theo nhi\u1ec1u th\u00f3i x\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a V-League. HLV Minh Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng cho bi\u1ebft c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL gi\u1edd c\u0169ng bi\u1ebft s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ec3u x\u1ea3o khi thi \u0111\u1ea5u, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ch\u01a1i \"r\u1eafn\" h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-viet-nam/bau-duc-len-tieng-ve-quyet-dinh-treo-gio-tang-tien-168-183657.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 255);\">T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eebng b\u1ecb b\u1ea7u \u0110\u1ee9c c\u1ea5m</span></span> h\u1ebft giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i v\u00ec pha b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Duy M\u1ea1nh. M\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \"ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169\". Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a HAGL l\u00e0 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh c\u0169ng b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 3 tr\u1eadn v\u00ec c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ba tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, HAGL to\u00e0n thua khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai r\u01a1i xu\u1ed1ng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 9 trong BXH V-League 2018. \u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, HAGL s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 v\u00e0o 17h00 (22/6).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/5/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/an-the-do-truc-tiep-cau-thu-hagl-nhan-an-phat-cuc-nang-291-183608.html\">\u0102n th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL nh\u1eadn \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t C\u1ef0C N\u1eb6NG</span><br>\r\nNgay sau tr\u1eadn thua th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb treo gi\u00f2 n\u1eeda m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i V-League 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3710","checkdouble":"188924"},{"date":"15:14 19/06","title":"V\u00ec Conte Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi 2 sao kh\u1ee7ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/vi-conte-chelsea-chua-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-2-sao-khung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri v\u00ec t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a Antonio Conte.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lewandowski v\u00e0 Michael Seri t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i Chelsea v\u00ec Conte</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, song vi\u1ec7c ch\u01b0a gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\"><br>\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng v\u00ec Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 sao kh\u1ee7ng v\u00ec Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/vi-conte-chelsea-chua-the-ky-hop-dong-voi-2-sao-khung.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>V\u00ec Conte, Chelsea ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Lewandowski</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo The Times, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 nh\u1eafm b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Robert Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111ang g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJean Michael Seri mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge, song vi\u1ec7c Chelsea v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c ai s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y lo l\u1eafng.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, n\u1ebfu chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a The Blues kh\u00f4ng s\u1edbm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Napoli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a Robert Lewandowski c\u0169ng v\u1eady. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1edbi Chelsea, song v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 anh c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c The The Blues v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef hay sa th\u1ea3i Conte khi\u1ebfn Lewandowski c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y b\u1ea5t an, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1edf l\u1ea1i Bayern ho\u1eb7c chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Real thay v\u00ec c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Stamford Bridge.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea s\u1ebd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c t\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t s\u1ebd sa th\u1ea3i Conte v\u00e0 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli, Maurizio Sarri. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maurizio Sarri\" title=\"Maurizio Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/ms.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ngay trong tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea s\u1ebd nh\u00f3m h\u1ecdp v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, The Blues ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi Conte.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m, Sarri s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau m\u00e0 m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. Ngo\u00e0i Lewandowski v\u00e0 Jean Michael Seri \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chelsea-mua-trung-ve-koulibaly-cua-napoli-172-182256.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea mua Koulibaly c\u1ee7a Napoli</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Sarri d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi t\u1eeb 120 \u0111\u1ebfn 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3709","checkdouble":"188922"},{"date":"15:50 19/06","title":"Unai Emery ch\u1ec9 t\u00ean 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/unai-emery-chi-ten-5-cai-ten-khong-the-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Unai Emery \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Arsenal, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean quan tr\u1ecdng, c\u1ef1u HLV PSG mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean n\u00e0y h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/Chuyen-nhuong-Arsenal-2018-khong-ban-5-cai-ten-nay-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery mu\u1ed1n Aubameyang v\u00e0 Lacazette kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eddi Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Hector Bellerin, chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean bao g\u1ed3m Alexandre Lacazette, Granit Xhaka, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Hector Bellerin.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y, Pierre Emerick Aubameyang, Henrikh Mkhitaryan v\u00e0 Alexandre Lacazette m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Arsenal kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eddi cho b\u1ed9 ba k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGranit Xhaka m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u1ee5y S\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Emirates. Hector Bellerin c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n g\u1eafn b\u00f3 l\u00e2u d\u00e0i v\u1edbi Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady c\u1ea3 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean m\u00e0 Unai Emery mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef \u0111\u1ec1u cam k\u1ebft t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u1edbi Arsenal, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh n\u00f2ng c\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Emery mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u00eam 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song song v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" title=\"Emery lam HLV Arsenal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/unai-emery-chi-ten-5-cai-ten-khong-the-roi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Emery mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1ea2Arsenal 2018 mua 3 t\u00e2n binh ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner t\u1eeb Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do, h\u1ecd \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 th\u1ee7&nbsp; m\u00f4n Bernd Leno v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018-172-188928.html\">Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo b\u00e1o ch\u00ed Italia, Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea9y m\u1ea1nh vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho Petr Cech.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean Emery c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/arsenal-sap-mua-duoc-sokratis-172-187253.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal mua trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund</span>, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3708","checkdouble":"188927"},{"date":"16:10 19/06","title":"Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao m\u1edbi n\u1ed5i \u1edf World Cup 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/liverpool-va-arsenal-dai-chien-vi-sao-moi-noi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hirving Lozano \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf b\u1ea3ng F World Cup 2018 gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Mexico b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u M\u1ef9 \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-0. Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u00fap Mexico \u0111\u1ee9ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Liverpool-muon-mua-Hirving-Lozano-cua-PSV-Eindhoven-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Lozano gi\u00fap \u0110T Mexico \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0110\u1ee9c 1-0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Hirving Lozano l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t cho Mexico, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua 2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o g\u00f3c g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0110\u1ee9c \u1edf World Cup 2018, Hirving Lozano c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ef1c cao trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSV Eindhoven. \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 Lan, nh\u01b0ng anh \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ghi 19 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 tung ra t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 11 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o PSV Eindhoven. S\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh nh\u01b0ng khi c\u1ea7n Lozano c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ed9 c\u00f4ng ho\u1eb7c trung phong c\u1eafm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lozano</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n mua Hirving Lozano c\u1ee7a PSV Eindhoven, Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111ang theo d\u00f5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Mexico. C\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lozano ghi ban mo ti so trong tran dau giua Duc vs Mexico.\" title=\"Lozano ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c vs Mexico.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Tin-nong-World-Cup-2018-ngay-186-Anh-manh,-nhung-van-kem-Bi-hinh-anh-4.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal v\u00e0 Liverpool mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Lozano</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/lyon-chinh-thuc-xac-minh-thuc-hu-vu-liverpool-mua-fekir-172-188158.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool kh\u00f3 mua Nabil Fekir</span> h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm Hirving Lozano nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. HLV Klopp \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1996, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Liverpool \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Anfield.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Hirving Lozano, HLV Unai Emery c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 gia nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i. Ngo\u00e0i Liverpool v\u00e0 Arsenal th\u00ec MU v\u00e0 Everton c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hirving Lozano.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo-172-188935.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo-172-188935.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o</span><br>\r\nLiverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u01a1\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n</div>\r\nPSV Eindhoven m\u1edbi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Lozano, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00e2n ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi PSV, s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Lozano cho ph\u00e9p c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3707","checkdouble":"188928"},{"date":"16:37 19/06","title":"Liverpool ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 b\u00e8o","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u01a1\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ea9y Daniel Sturridge kh\u1ecfi Anfield</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Daniel Sturridge g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p g\u00ec v\u00e0o th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i anh kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/1/26/liverpool-chot-gia-ban-sturridge-voi-gia-beo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Sturridge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRoberto Firmino l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Liverpool \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed HLV Klopp c\u00f2n \u01b0u ti\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng Dominic Solanke h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh. Ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, Sturridge \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi West Brom theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u00ec nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ngh\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/klopp-buong-loi-cay-dang-voi-sturridge-172-178858.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge</span> \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn nh\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Klopp \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u00e1n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Sturridge</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd The Telegraph, West Brom mu\u1ed1n mua \u0111\u1ee9t Sturridge, song vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho West Brom.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool mu\u1ed1n b\u00e1n Daniel Sturridge v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/21/Liverpool-giam-gia-ban-tien-dao-Daniel-Sturridge-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Sturridge</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i, trong \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Sevilla v\u00e0 Fenerbahce. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi ra 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea v\u00e0 Man City. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf ch\u1ed7 Sturridge v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. Hi\u1ec7n ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t t\u00e2n binh Wolvehampton l\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Sturridge. Vi\u1ec7c th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan ng\u1ea1i khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Wolvehampton \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho Sturridge m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao. N\u1ebfu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y, b\u1edfi Sturridge c\u00f3 kinh nghi\u1ec7m thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3706","checkdouble":"188935"},{"date":"16:56 19/06","title":"\u0110\u00e2y! B\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Wilshere n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Arsenal","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/18/day-ben-do-moi-cua-wilshere-neu-roi-arsenal.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Jack Wilshere v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1o h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a quy\u1ebft\u00a0\u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh hay kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/18/day-ben-do-moi-cua-wilshere-neu-roi-arsenal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilshere v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a bi\u1ebft s\u1ebd ra \u0111i hay \u1edf l\u1ea1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Daily Mail, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi. Theo \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-se-chot-tuong-lai-sau-cuoc-gap-hlv-emery-172-188179.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wilshere s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Emery \u0111\u1ec3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</span>.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Ramsey v\u00e0 Xhaka, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 2 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a Arsenal. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Torreira v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 26.4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Southampton \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Wilshere</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Jack Wilshere t\u1edbi Southampton \u0111ang l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary \u0111ang l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Wilshere tran Arsenal vs Atletico\" title=\"Wilshere tran Arsenal vs Atletico\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/27/Gareth-Southgate-phat-bieu-ve-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Southampton mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Wilshere\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMirror kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Southampton \u0111\u00e3 b\u00ed m\u1eadt \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 100.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Wilshere d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u01b0ng v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0y, n\u1ebfu chia tay Arsenal nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng anh s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Southampton. Ngo\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n St Mary th\u00ec nh\u1eefng West Ham, Wolves, Sampdoria v\u00e0 AC Milan c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3i th\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u00f3n ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y khi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, khi \u0111\u00f3 Southampton, West Ham v\u00e0 Wolves s\u1ebd c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3705","checkdouble":"188936"},{"date":"11:40 19/06","title":"B\u1ecb v\u1ee3 c\u1ea5m, ch\u00e0ng C\u0110V Mexico v\u1eabn \"l\u01b0\u1ee3n l\u1edd\" kh\u1eafp World Cup 2018 nh\u1edd h\u1ed9i b\u1ea1n \"l\u1ea7y l\u1ed9i\"","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/bi-vo-cam-chang-cdv-mexico-van-luon-lo-khap-world-cup-2018-nho-hoi-ban-lay-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m fan Mexico n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap anh ch\u00e0ng C\u0110V t\u1ed9i nghi\u1ec7p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c an \u1ee7i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o.\r\n</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">World Cup l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, di\u1ec5n ra 4 n\u0103m m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n. M\u1ecdi C\u0110V \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1t khao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp t\u1eadn h\u01b0\u1edfng b\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed World Cup, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t khi \u0110TQG c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o VCK.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng anh ch\u00e0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 t\u00ean Javier s\u1ed1ng t\u1ea1i Mexico l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i m\u01a1 \u01b0\u1edbc do v\u1ee3 c\u1ea5m c\u1eeda. \u0110\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Javier ph\u1ea5n ch\u1ea5n h\u01a1n, nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n g\u1ed3m 7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ecd mua m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc xe bus c\u0169, g\u1eedi theo \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn B\u0110N. Nh\u1eadn xe t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u1ee7a Ronaldo, nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n n\u00e0y l\u00e1i xuy\u00ean qua ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ecba \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i Nga m\u00e0 Mexico thi \u0111\u1ea5u. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean in h\u00ecnh Javier v\u1edbi k\u00edch c\u1ee1 si\u00eau l\u1edbn v\u00e0 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh g\u1eedi v\u1ec1, gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng c\u1ea3 nh\u00f3m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 th\u1ebf l\u00e0 \"Javier\" xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t qu\u00e1n bar t\u1ea1i Amsterdam, m\u1ed9t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n \u1edf \u0110\u1ee9c, u\u1ed1ng bia, l\u00e1i xe v\u00e0 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 h\u00f2a nh\u1ecbp v\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ea1i Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1eafc h\u1eb3n \u1edf nh\u00e0, anh ch\u00e0ng Javier \"x\u1ecbn\" r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ebfn \u0111i c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u00e0nh c\u00f9ng \u0110T Mexico k\u00e9o d\u00e0i c\u00e0ng l\u00e2u c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t, cho \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1eb9n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 SV\u0110 Luzhniki, n\u01a1i t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/photo-2-15293355895291528109243.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/photo-1-15293355895241897612728.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/photo-1-15293355870691569739307.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3704","checkdouble":"188915"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup cho \u0111\u1ea1i gia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. D\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ea1i gia Italia v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang n\u1ed5i \u0111\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e1m t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga khan hi\u1ebfm nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i, Aleksandr Golovin n\u1ed5i l\u00ean nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, \u201cNh\u1eefng ch\u00fa g\u1ea5u\u201d \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ho\u00e0nh tr\u00e1ng 5-0. \u1ede \u0111\u00f3, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 22 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 n\u00e9t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGolovin \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 2 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Nga t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 ph\u1ea1t tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c v\u00e0 cho th\u1ea5y \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf CSKA Moscow. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/cska-tu-choi-ban-golovin-cho-juventus.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o tuy\u1ec3n Nga</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n27 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho CSKA t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Nga, Golovin c\u00f3 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f9ng 1 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. \u1ede c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 h\u1ed9i t\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ee7 nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng, ki\u1ebfn thi\u1ebft, \u0111i b\u00f3ng cho t\u1edbi s\u00fat xa.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus mu\u1ed1n Golovin nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Golovin t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Nga th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u vang d\u1ed9i t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Juventus t\u1eeb suy ngh\u0129 mang anh v\u1ec1 \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn th\u00e0nh h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. H\u1ecd g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u Euro t\u1edbi CSKA \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eaft x\u00edch m\u00ecnh mu\u1ed1n b\u1ed5 sung.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" title=\"tien ve Aleksandr Golovin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/Juventus-muon-mua-Aleksandr-Golovin-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebfc r\u1eb1ng l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c CSKA t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n Golovin cho Juventus. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 thu v\u1ec1 \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 25 tri\u1ec7u Euro sau th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i v\u1ed9i v\u00e0ng khi c\u00f3 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Golovin. M\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e1 gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c b\u00ean s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn CSKA \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u00f2n Juventus, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u1eabu ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 c\u01a1 b\u1eafp nh\u01b0 Sami Khedira, Blaise Matuidi hay Stefano Sturaro, Bianconeri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 Miralem Pjanic trong kh\u00e2u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ecd tin c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Rodrigo Bentancur ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Aleksandr Golovin tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhm-arsenal-nhan-hlv-unai-emery-hay-ngay-lap-tuc-mua-golovin-172-188557.html\">NHM Arsenal nh\u1eafn HLV Unai Emery: H\u00e3y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c mua Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Arsenal mua Aleksandr Golovin, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea3o NHM Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7 sau khi ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nga t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Saudi Arabia.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-nga-50-saudi-arabia-diem-10-cho-aleksandr-golovin-421-188547.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nga 5-0 Saudi Arabia: \u0110i\u1ec3m 10 cho Aleksandr Golovin</span><br>\r\n<span>Tr\u1eadn Nga vs Saudi Arabia b\u1ea3ng A World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ch\u00ednh phong \u0111\u1ed9 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i...</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3703","checkdouble":"188909"},{"date":"10:21 19/06","title":"Barca b\u1ecb sao Ajax n\u00f3i l\u1eddi cay \u0111\u1eafng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf cho Andres Iniesta trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>C\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ebft th\u00fac m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18, Andres Iniesta \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay v\u1edbi Barcelona. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 34 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 nh\u01b0 x\u01b0a v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb. Iniesta kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang Vissel Kobe c\u1ee7a Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, m\u1ed9t CLB c\u00f3 c\u00f9ng nh\u00e0 t\u00e0i tr\u1ee3 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia, h\u1ecd bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft tay v\u00e0o t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Trong danh s\u00e1ch n\u00e0y c\u00f3 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u00e1i t\u00ean c\u00f3 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng bao g\u1ed3m t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Frenkie de Jong c\u1ee7a Ajax. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi tr\u00f4i qua ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 21 tu\u1ed5i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin d\u00f9ng \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i 1 CLB c\u00f3 ti\u1ebfng t\u1ea1i H\u00e0 Lan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca c\u1ea7n De Jong thay th\u1ebf Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Jong c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 22 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n (6 t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb) v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 7 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o. Nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t to\u00e0n di\u1ec7n c\u1ea3 trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng l\u1eabn d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1eeb xa c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb H\u00e0 Lan khi\u1ebfn Barca ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>B\u1ecb De Jong t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi t\u1edd Goal, De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Blaugrana h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n anh l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p h\u1eefu \u00edch cho hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 21 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" title=\"Frenkie de Jong cua Ajax\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/de-jong-khong-muon-toi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">De Jong kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Barca trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c<em>Th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ecdc b\u00e1o T\u00e2y Ban Nha</em>\u201d, De Jong n\u00f3i. \u201c<em>\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u1eefng tin \u0111\u1ed3n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ee9c t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i qu\u00e1 ch\u00fa t\u00e2m v\u00e0o n\u00f3. T\u00f4i giao n\u00f3 cho \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft li\u1ec7u \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111ang suy ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y hay kh\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng.</em>\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i De Jong, Barca c\u0169ng \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Trong \u0111\u00f3, ti\u00eau bi\u1ec3u l\u00e0 Ilkay Gundogan c\u1ee7a Man City d\u00f9 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-muon-trao-doi-nguoi-voi-tottenham-180-188303.html\">Barca mu\u1ed1n trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi Tottenham</span><br>\r\n<span>Barca mu\u1ed1n mua Christian Eriksen c\u1ee7a Tottenham, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n c\u1ed9ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Rafinha \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Spurs nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/ivan-rakitic-noi-gi-truoc-vien-canh-neymar-cap-ben-real-madrid-180-188263.html\">Ivan Rakitic n\u00f3i g\u00ec tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh Neymar c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid?</span><br>\r\n<span>Ivan Rakitic ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Neymar, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 \u1edf Barca s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng r\u1eddi PSG c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3702","checkdouble":"188908"},{"date":"09:56 19/06","title":"Man City ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli. Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Sky Sports, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Etihad s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Man City li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Jorginho l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1eeb l\u00e2u. \u0110\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u00fd k\u1ebft. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang ch\u1edd 2 CLB \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed3ng thu\u1eadn, bao g\u1ed3m c\u1ea3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thanh to\u00e1n, ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed v\u00e0 l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/26/man-city-sap-co-jorginho-cua-napoli.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Napoli gi\u00e1 46,5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho m\u1edbi \u0111\u0103ng m\u1ed9t t\u1ea5m \u1ea3nh tr\u00ean Instagram v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 c\u00f9ng gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Brazil. Anh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd bay t\u1edbi Manchester ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf khi n\u00e0o 2 CLB th\u1ed1ng nh\u1ea5t chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 37 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n cho Napoli m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng bao g\u1ed3m 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00ednh Man City t\u1ea1i Champions League h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Verona tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Napoli n\u0103m 2014. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i nhanh ch\u00f3ng tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf n\u01a1i tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. K\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u ph\u1ed1i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Jorginho gi\u00fap l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a Napoli th\u00eam ph\u1ea7n m\u1ec1m m\u1ea1i v\u00e0 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMan City c\u1ee7a HLV Pep Guardiola c\u0169ng ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Yaya Toure m\u1edbi ra \u0111i sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf v\u00e0 Jorginho l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. Guardiola r\u1ea5t th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Italia v\u00e0 tin anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Man City tr\u00ean trang Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/soc-raheem-sterling-tu-choi-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-man-city-172-188324.html\">S\u1ed1c: Raheem Sterling t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/doi-bong-dau-tien-dam-phan-voi-yaya-toure-172-188052.html\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Yaya Toure</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/neymar-tha-thinh-man-city-pep-van-rat-tinh-don-172-187954.html\">Neymar \u201cth\u1ea3 th\u00ednh\u201d Man City, Pep v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t t\u1ec9nh \u0111\u00f2n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3701","checkdouble":"188904"},{"date":"10:42 19/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir l\u1ea1i m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/29/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-fekir-lai-moi-goi-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nabil Fekir kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nguy\u00ean c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1n nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea5y m\u1ef1c</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/liverpool-nang-gia-hoi-mua-sao-tuyen-phap-len-60-trieu-bang-172-187260.html\" target=\"_blank\">Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Fekir</span> v\u00e0 t\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao n\u00e0y v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 6. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00e0 The Kop bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Fekir \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n v\u1edbi Liverpool. Nh\u01b0ng ph\u00eda Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Fekir s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/29/nguoi-dai-dien-cua-fekir-lai-moi-goi-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Fekir m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu v\u1eady, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Jean-Pierre Bernes m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ea1i trao th\u00eam hy v\u1ecdng cho Liverpool trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. Khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c Liverpool theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Fekir, Bernes cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cFekir kh\u00f4ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u00ec\u2026 (Bernes \u1ea5p \u00fang), m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac. C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n nh\u01b0 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a k\u1ebft th\u00fac\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Lyon quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Fekir</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng n\u00e0y, Lyon kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng x\u1ea3y ra.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cLyon mu\u1ed1n th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Liverpool v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. V\u00e0 Lyon \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u ch\u1ea5m h\u1ebft cho v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n n\u00e0y v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cM\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Fekir mong mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Liverpool nh\u01b0ng Lyon v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19, khi m\u00e0 Lyon s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i Champions League sau khi c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua\u201d.</em><br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Nabil Fekir \u0111ang tham d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean sau khi v\u00e0o s\u00e2n t\u1eeb gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Australia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Fekir:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/5-cau-thu-ma-liverpool-co-the-mua-thay-vi-nabil-fekir-172-188319.html\">5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Liverpool c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 mua thay v\u00ec Nabil Fekir</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/lyon-chinh-thuc-xac-minh-thuc-hu-vu-liverpool-mua-fekir-172-188158.html\">Lyon ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c minh th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Liverpool mua Fekir</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3700","checkdouble":"188906"},{"date":"11:03 19/06","title":"Arsenal s\u1eafp c\u00f3 t\u00e2n binh th\u1ee9 2 h\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin t\u1eeb n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c, Arsenal \u0111ang ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u1edbi ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh Bernd Leno c\u1ee7a Bayer Leverkusen.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsenal ti\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n Bernd Leno</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bernd Leno trong v\u00f2ng 48 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/arsenal-sap-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-bernd-leno.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal s\u1eafp chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bernd Leno</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Leno \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 304 l\u1ea7n cho Bayer Leverkusen k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y n\u0103m 2011. Nh\u01b0ng theo tin \u0111\u1ed3n, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Arsenal tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u01b0\u1ee3c bi\u1ebft, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed r\u01a1i v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. HLV Unai Emery \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf Petr Cech ngay m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i ti\u1ebfp theo. T\u1edd Bild kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Arsenal s\u1ebd ra m\u1eaft th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y t\u1edbi.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng n\u00e0y, Cech nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Th\u1ea7n g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi CH S\u00e9c nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd chia tay s\u00e2n Emirates \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1t \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 h\u00e8</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cho \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac n\u00e0y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/nong-arsenal-chinh-thuc-don-tan-binh-dau-tien-duoi-thoi-emery-172-187828.html\" target=\"_blank\">Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Stephan Lichtsteiner</span>. C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Juventus gia nh\u1eadp \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do. Anh \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd k\u00fd v\u00e0o h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m v\u1edbi The Gunners.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trung v\u1ec7 Sokratis Papastathopoulos nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Emirates sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t bu\u1ed5i ki\u1ec3m tra y t\u1ebf. Cha c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 r\u1eb1ng Sokratis \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Manchester United \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201c\u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb Man United. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 7 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d, Charalambos Papastathopoulos chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t k\u00eanh radio c\u1ee7a Hy L\u1ea1p.<br>\r\n<br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</em></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><em>\u201cMan United c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi Dortmund. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Sokratis kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u01b0ng con trai t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn Arsenal\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam tin t\u1ee9c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Arsenal:<br>\r\n</strong>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/granit-xhaka-gia-han-hop-dong-voi-arsenal-172-188587.html\">Tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/arsenal-chieu-mo-torreira-tuong-lai-bat-dau-tu-hom-nay-172-188414.html\">Arsenal chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Torreira: T\u01b0\u01a1ng lai b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb h\u00f4m nay</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3699","checkdouble":"188910"}]}